      <abstract id="aspace_fc3db9306bb888c44f1bcd8df6308856">Elon Clark was a professor in the Duke
        Medical Center's Division of Audiovisual Education. His collection includes drawings,
        sketches, correspondence and other materials used to design the Duke University shield,
        mace, academic gowns, flags and university colors.</abstract>
